      "instruction": "<p>Return the pan to a medium heat with a generous drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong></p>\n<p><span class=\"text-highlight\">Add the <strong>cumin seeds</strong> and <strong>fennel seeds </strong></span>and cook for 1-2 min or until fragrant</p>\n<p>Meanwhile, re-boil a kettle</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>",
