      "instruction": "<p>Once fragrant, add the <strong>spice paste</strong> and<strong> tomato paste </strong>and cook for 2-3 min further</p>\n<p>Add the<strong> drained potatoes, </strong>200ml<span class=\"text-danger\"> [300ml]</span> <strong>boiled water </strong>and the<span class=\"text-highlight\"> <strong>vegetable stock cube<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong></span> and cook for 3-4 min</p>\n<p>Meanwhile, chop the <strong>coriander </strong>finely, including the stalks</p>",
